00:16:05.836 --> 00:16:07.896 A:middle
The first is to fail gracefully.

00:16:08.546 --> 00:16:09.906 A:middle
It's possible you'll be provided

00:16:09.906 --> 00:16:11.246 A:middle
with URLs that represent

00:16:11.246 --> 00:16:12.746 A:middle
outdated, invalid, or

00:16:12.746 --> 00:16:13.986 A:middle
nonexistent content.

00:16:14.666 --> 00:16:15.566 A:middle
If you determine that a

00:16:15.566 --> 00:16:16.986 A:middle
universal link can't be opened

00:16:16.986 --> 00:16:18.716 A:middle
by your app, you can often open

00:16:18.716 --> 00:16:19.966 A:middle
it in Safari View Controller.

00:16:20.396 --> 00:16:21.776 A:middle
This keeps the user engaged in

00:16:21.776 --> 00:16:22.156 A:middle
your app.

00:16:22.836 --> 00:16:24.176 A:middle
If Safari View Controller is not

00:16:24.176 --> 00:16:26.006 A:middle
an option, consider opening the

00:16:26.006 --> 00:16:28.126 A:middle
URL in Safari, or at a minimum,

00:16:28.336 --> 00:16:29.696 A:middle
prompting with details about the

00:16:29.696 --> 00:16:30.146 A:middle
issue.

00:16:30.606 --> 00:16:31.946 A:middle
Avoid sending the user to a

00:16:31.946 --> 00:16:32.686 A:middle
blank screen.

00:16:33.716 --> 00:16:35.316 A:middle
If the user is visiting your

00:16:35.316 --> 00:16:37.016 A:middle
website, use the Smart App

00:16:37.016 --> 00:16:38.506 A:middle
Banner to provide a link either

00:16:38.506 --> 00:16:39.806 A:middle
to the App Store or to your

00:16:39.806 --> 00:16:40.346 A:middle
content.

00:16:40.816 --> 00:16:42.116 A:middle
The Smart App Banner integrates

00:16:42.116 --> 00:16:43.616 A:middle
seamlessly with Safari and looks

00:16:43.616 --> 00:16:44.016 A:middle
great.

00:16:44.436 --> 00:16:45.666 A:middle
And there's no JavaScript or

00:16:45.666 --> 00:16:47.146 A:middle
custom URL schemes required to

00:16:47.146 --> 00:16:47.676 A:middle
support it.

00:16:48.756 --> 00:16:50.306 A:middle
Finally, if you have feedback on

00:16:50.306 --> 00:16:51.426 A:middle
how we can improve universal

00:16:51.426 --> 00:16:53.016 A:middle
links, I would love to hear it.

00:16:53.366 --> 00:16:54.396 A:middle
Please use the feedback

00:16:54.396 --> 00:16:55.786 A:middle
assistant and let us know what

00:16:55.786 --> 00:16:56.966 A:middle
we can do to make universal

00:16:56.966 --> 00:16:57.836 A:middle
links even better.

00:16:58.466 --> 00:16:59.176 A:middle
Thank you.
